Welcome

Run this project you have to install these packeges

express , cors , mongodb , dotenv , body-parser , uuid , and

you can install nodemon for automatic restart the server if any changes

All Scripts are

To run the project with nodemon you can type --- npm run dev
run without nodemon with simple node ---------- npm run start

------All API Details are here you can test these api on thunder client , postman also

-get single data--- GET --- http://localhost:5050/api/v3/app/events/:id paste here event id in the place of :\_id
--get all data --- GET ----- http://localhost:5050/api/v3/app/
-- add New data ---- POST ------ http://localhost:5050/api/v3/app/events
--update data---- PATCH ----- http://localhost:5050/api/v3/app/events/:id --- paste here event id in the place of :\_id
--Delete data-- DELETE -- http://localhost:5050/api/v3/app/events/:id --- paste here event id in the place of :\_id

